    <string name="settings_changelog_title">View changelog</string>
    <string name="settings_changelog_body">Motoko v1.1\n\n- Redesigned UI &amp; UX: Unified bottom sheet headers, high-contrast dashed input fields, and updated card styles.\n- Font &amp; Accessibility Support: Adaptive layout scaling for large fonts, text truncation, and multiline form field support.\n- Customization &amp; Navigation: Alignment options for floating action menus, navigation bar placement, and toggleable colored elements.\n- Fixes &amp; Smooth Animations: Opaque transaction card backgrounds during swipe-to-delete with automatic reset when cancelling deletion.</string>
